Is there a token on hand?

Source: R/gs4_auth.R
gs4_has_token.Rd

Reports whether googlesheets4 has stored a token, ready for use in downstream requests.

gs4_has_token()

Value

Logical.

See also

Other low-level API functions: gs4_token(), request_generate(), request_make()

Examples

gs4_has_token()

#> [1] FALSE
